What you need to know:  Early this week, Tanzania’s Serengeti Girls beat giants Cameroon 5-1 to seal their spot in the Fifa Under-17 World CupTanzania has always struggled to raise teams for major tournaments, including the Olympics, but it seems they are carving out a niche for themselves in women’s footballWhatever happens at the U-17 World Cup in in India come October, I will be cheering the Tanzanian girls and praying they excel where my country has failed